---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Roadmaps" description="Structured AI agent learning paths — from zero to production.">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h1>🗺️ Roadmaps</h1>
      <p>Structured learning paths so you always know what to study next. From your first agent to enterprise-grade multi-agent systems.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid">
      <a href="/roadmaps/zero-to-ai-agent" class="card">
        <div class="card-level beginner">Beginner</div>
        <h3>Zero to AI Agent</h3>
        <p>Start from scratch. Understand what agents are, how LLMs work as a brain, and build your first functional agent.</p>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag">LLMs</span><span class="tag">Tools</span><span class="tag">LangChain</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/roadmaps/se-to-ai-engineer" class="card">
        <div class="card-level intermediate">Intermediate</div>
        <h3>Software Engineer → AI Engineer</h3>
        <p>Leverage your existing SE skills. A 3-month roadmap based on Zahere's own transition journey at Dell.</p>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag">GenAI</span><span class="tag">MLOps</span><span class="tag">System Design</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/roadmaps/production-agents" class="card">
        <div class="card-level advanced">Advanced</div>
        <h3>Production-Grade Agents</h3>
        <p>Move beyond prototypes. Observability, reliability, human-in-the-loop, and deploying agents at scale.</p>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag">LangGraph</span><span class="tag">Observability</span><span class="tag">Scale</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/roadmaps/agentic-rag" class="card">
        <div class="card-level intermediate">Intermediate</div>
        <h3>Agentic RAG Mastery</h3>
        <p>Go beyond naive RAG. Build agents that retrieve, reason, and synthesize information intelligently.</p>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag">RAG</span><span class="tag">Vector DBs</span><span class="tag">Retrieval</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .card-level { font-size: 0.72rem; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .beginner { color: #00ff88; } .intermediate { color: #f59e0b; } .advanced { color: #ef4444; }
  .card h3 { font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .card p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .card-tags { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
</style>
